> 

> IMO, if you want to give individual Players the authority to issue binding
> orders to enforce the terms of a personal agreement, the Rules need to
> acknowledge the existence of personal agreements as a source of that authority.
>  By "binding order" I mean an order that carries a Rule based (in-game) penalty
